column5: Anyone know where I could find a boat launch in Hay Bay ?

Shermans Launch is at the end of Bayview Road off of County Road 9  http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&source=s_q&hl=en&geocode=&q=bayview+road,+napanee&sll=49.891235,-97.15369&sspn=46.570406,79.013672&ie=UTF8&hq=&hnear=Bayview+Dr,+Napanee,+Lennox+and+Addington+County,+Ontario+K7R+3K8&z=16
